keystone.api

Class Keystone

  • java.lang.Object
    • keystone.api.Keystone

  • public class Keystone
extends java.lang.Object
    Base Keystone API class, used to retrieve Modules, retrieve global state, and toggle whether Keystone is active. Also contains Logger and Random instance
